c: 16
v: 113
t: "wlqd 'ursil allah 'iilaa 'ahl \"mk\" rasulana mnhm, hu alnabii muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm, yaerifun nsbh wsdqh wamanth, falam yqblu ma ja'ahum bh, walam ysdqwh, fa'akhadhahum aleadhab min alshdayd waljue walkhwf, wqatl ezmayhm fi \"bdr\" wahum zalimun lanfshm balshrk ballh, walsdd ean sbylh"